{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487014339,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_rBt43CLMJ0sfTsRnzEuoRu4l","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl","offset":1,"limit":20},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T04:58:44Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3\",\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\"},\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-3-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}\n2: {\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"spec_check_result\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"folder_state\":\"spec-present\",\"normalized_topic\":\"validate and stress test the merge design for folding deep loop runtime into deep loop workflows as system deep loop structural layout bidirectional path coupling repair the system spec kit tooling borrow reference migration across commands agents readmes advisor corpus and whether fallback router ts should be wired for real glm 5 2 to mimo v2 5 pro fallback\",\"specPath\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/spec.md\",\"lockPath\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/.deep-research.lock\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T04:58:44Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-3-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1}\n3: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"run\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Structural layout and bidirectional path-coupling repair\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.86,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly confirmed the candidate layout and path rules, while adding a concrete missed WORKSPACE_ROOT repair in render-command-contract.cjs.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Is the proposed system-deep-loop/runtime structural layout correct?\",\"Are forward and reverse path-coupling repair rules correct at concrete call sites?\",\"Is the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow repair correctly scoped and sufficient?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The runtime-as-infrastructure layout is correct and should not become a workflow mode.\",\"The asymmetric path rule is correct, with one added root-depth repair for render-command-contract.cjs.\",\"The system-spec-kit tooling-borrow is load-bearing and belongs in the structural phase.\"],\"keyFindings\":[{\"id\":\"f001-runtime-not-mode\",\"summary\":\"system-deep-loop/runtime should remain infrastructure, not a workflow mode.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md:12\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json:19\"]},{\"id\":\"f002-forward-rule-mostly-correct\",\"summary\":\"Forward runtime-to-hub shared references keep hop-count and delete the old sibling segment.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs:8\"]},{\"id\":\"f003-render-root-depth-missed\",\"summary\":\"render-command-contract.cjs has a WORKSPACE_ROOT depth constant that must gain one more parent hop after nesting.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs:13\"]},{\"id\":\"f004-reverse-rule-confirmed\",\"summary\":\"Workflow packet code moves one hop closer to runtime and should target ../../runtime or ../../../runtime depending on nested depth.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/de... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n\n(End of file - total 3 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T04:58:44Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3\",\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\"},\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-3-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"ev