:\"Active system-spec-kit eval fixtures intentionally contain historical old-name queries/decoys and should be reviewed or allowlisted, not blindly renamed.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/eval/data/ground-truth.json:795\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/eval/data/ground-truth.json:960\"]},{\"id\":\"f012-graph-edge-collapse\",\"summary\":\"Sibling graph metadata needs edge collapse from two old identities to one system-deep-loop identity.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/graph-metadata.json:35\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/graph-metadata.json:40\"]}],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Blind repo-wide find/replace of old skill names\",\"reason\":\"Generated contracts, advisor fields, graph edges, and historical eval fixtures need different handling.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/eval/data/ground-truth.json:795\"}],\"recommendedNextFocus\":\"Evaluate fallback-router.ts and current fanout retry behavior.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:05:18Z\",\"durationMs\":520000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-3-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1}\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl\n@@ -1,3 +1,4 @@\n {\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into de