{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487285519,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","part":{"id":"prt_f401fda9e0017wk1kIZ8oeRGN8","messageID":"msg_f401fa714001aRq3cmspHD0Fbn","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute detached deep-research lineage `gpt55-fast-3` for system-deep-loop unification research and write all outputs under its lineage artifact directory.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Write only under `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind artifact_dir directly to the override.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop` to convergence or `config.maxIterations: 10`, then `phase_synthesis`.\n- Final output when complete must be exactly `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-3`.\n- Detached session id: `fanout-gpt55-fast-3-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Stop policy: `convergence`; minimum convergence floor from workflow refs: 3 iterations.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md` and workflow/state/convergence refs.\n- Initialized lineage directories: `prompts/`, `iterations/`, `deltas/`, `dispatch-receipts/`.\n- Created lineage state files:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deep-research-strategy.md`\n  - `deep-research-findings-registry.json`\n  - `deep-research-dashboard.md`\n- Completed iteration 1:\n  - `prompts/iteration-001.md`\n  - `iterations/iteration-001.md`\n  - `deltas/iter-001.jsonl`\n  - Updated state/strategy/registry/dashboard.\n- Verified iteration 1 with:\n  - `node \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/verify-iteration.cjs\" --loop-type research --artifact-dir \".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3\" --iteration 1 --json`\n  - Output: `{\"ok\":true,\"reason\":null,\"detail\":\"iteration 1 complete: narrative + route-proof + delta\"}`\n- Began iteration 2 external-reference migration scan.\n\n### In Progress\n- Iteration 2 focus: inventory external reference migration categories and stress-test child 003 coverage across executable, generated, advisor, agent, README, hook, CI, plugin, and graph surfaces.\n- Last timestamp fetched before writing iteration 2: `2026-07-08T05:05:18Z`.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Did not spawn nested `opencode run`; current session is treated as the detached lineage.\n- Did not run `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs` because it lacks an artifact-dir override and would resolve/write canonical `{spec_folder}/research`.\n- Used manual reducer-equivalent writes inside the lineage directory only.\n- `resource-map.md` is absent for the target spec; state records `resource_map_present: false` and strategy notes `resource-map.md not present; skipping coverage gate`.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Write iteration 2 prompt, narrative, delta, and append iteration record to `deep-research-state.jsonl`.\n- Update strategy/registry/dashboard with iteration 2 findings.\n- Run `verify-iteration.cjs` for iteration 2.\n- Continue iterations until legal convergence after at least 3 iterations or max 10.\n- Run synthesis and final artifact verification.\n- Output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-3`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Iteration 1 findings:\n  - `system-deep-loop/runtime/` should remain infrastructure, not a workflow mode.\n  - Bidirectional path-coupling repair is directionally correct.\n  - Forward runtime-to-hub shared refs should remove `deep-loop-workflows` segment while preserving hop-count.\n  - Reverse workflow-to-runtime refs should move one hop closer and target `runtime/`.\n  - New correction: `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs:13` has `WORKSPACE_ROOT` depth that must gain one extra `..` after nesting.\n  - `system-spec-kit` tooling-borrow is load-bearing: runtime typecheck and council test discovery depend on current paths.\n- Iteration 2 scan counts:\n  - `all_non_history_files`: `776`\n  - `commands_deep_files`: `20`\n  - `doctor_files`: `5`\n  - `opencode_agents`: `5`\n  - `claude_agents`: `5`\n  - `advisor_files`: `30`\n  - `system_spec_kit_files`: `43`\n- Additional iteration 2 surfaces found:\n  - `.opencode/hooks/README.md` references old workflow path.\n  - `.github/workflows/agent-mirror-sync.yml` references old workflow path.\n  - `.opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js` hardcodes `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json`.\n  - `.opencode/plugins/tests/mk-deep-loop-guard.test.cjs` creates fixture under `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows`.\n  - Generated command contracts under `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/*.contract.md` contain old paths and generated headers.\n  - `system-skill-advisor` hardcodes advisor projections to `deep-loop-workflows`.\n  - Some historical/eval references should not be blindly renamed, e.g. `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/eval/data/ground-truth.json:795` query `\"give me the full set of deep-loop-workflows consolidation phase specs\"`.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3`: detached lineage artifact boundary.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only lineage state.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/iterations/iteration-001.md`: completed iteration 1 evidence.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deltas/iter-001.jsonl`: iteration 1 delta/route proof.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md`: structural merge candidate plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md`: reference migration candidate plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/004-fallback-router-wiring/plan.md`: optional fallback-router wiring plan.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs`: missed `WORKSPACE_ROOT` depth repair.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/compile-command-contracts.cjs`: known `WORKSPACE_ROOT` depth repair.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs`: current workflow-to-runtime relative import example.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/vitest.config.ts`: runtime test discovery path.\n- `.opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js`: plugin hardcoded mode registry path.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_research.contract.md`: generated contract with old paths.","time":{"start":1783487257246,"end":1783487285516},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0035d5a5df4a1ab8016a4ddb193f4881919a3c12e84f7c70cd","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
