{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487394312,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","part":{"id":"prt_f4021f1ab0010L9BYMV1ZbZDiS","messageID":"msg_f4021dc4e001j7emNHmubocwLS","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","type":"text","text":"Iteration 3 conclusion: child 004 should remain optional/deferred unless the operator explicitly wants behavior expansion. A safe implementation needs registry/schema work and a caller at `fanout-run.cjs`, not just a small edit in `fanout-pool.cjs`.","time":{"start":1783487394219,"end":1783487394311},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0766e3eed91b3d28016a4ddba238748191a542f807257379c5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
