\":\"Confirmed most migration categories and added two refinements: fresh Stage-A baseline authority and explicit allowlisting for historical active eval fixtures.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Is external reference migration complete and safely staged across commands, agents, READMEs, hooks, advisor corpus, and graph metadata?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"External reference migration is broadly complete and safely staged if Stage A is treated as authoritative and historical eval fixtures are reviewed or allowlisted instead of blindly renamed.\"],\"keyFindings\":[{\"id\":\"f006-stage-a-live-baseline\",\"summary\":\"Live old-name inventory differs from the spec count; Stage A must capture the authoritative baseline immediately before edits.\",\"sources\":[\"command: rg-count sweep 2026-07-08T05:02Z\"]},{\"id\":\"f007-compiled-contracts-regenerate-only\",\"summary\":\"Compiled /deep command contracts embed generated headers, source digests, and old paths, so they must be regenerated rather than hand-edited.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_research.contract.md:1\",\".opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_research.contract.md:6\"]},{\"id\":\"f008-advisor-field-scope\",\"summary\":\"Advisor constants and routing fixtures require field-scoped migration plus accuracy re-baseline.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:83\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts:109\"]},{\"id\":\"f009-plugin-fixture-pair\",\"summary\":\"mk-deep-loop-guard's registry path and test fixture must update together.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js:35\",\".opencode/plugins/tests/mk-deep-loop-guard.test.cjs:25... (line truncated to 2000 chars)","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":4,"totalLines":4,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"star