rence migration coverage | 0.72 | 7 | complete |\n| 3 | Fallback-router wiring scope | 0.44 | 7 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n5/5 answered. Remaining: synthesis-readiness convergence pass.\n\n## Convergence Trend\n0.86 -> 0.72 -> 0.44 (novelty declining; minimum iteration floor met, but run one convergence pass before synthesis).\n\n## Dead Ends\n| Approach | Reason | Evidence | Iteration |\n|---|---|---|---:|\n| Add `runtime/` as a workflow mode | Runtime is backend infrastructure; workflow modes are separately modeled in `mode-registry.json`. | `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json:19` | 1 |\n| Blind repo-wide find/replace | Generated contracts, advisor fields, graph edges, and historical eval fixtures need different handling. | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/eval/data/ground-truth.json:795` | 2 |\n| Mandatory child 004 in structural merge | Fallback wiring is behavior expansion requiring registry/schema, approval, model-id normalization, and attribution changes. | `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/004-fallback-router-wiring/spec.md:42` | 3 |\n\n## Next Focus\nSynthesis-readiness convergence pass, then final synthesis if no contradictions appear.","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":24,"totalLines":24,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-3/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1783487618506,"end":1783487618513}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_096048360aa52ef1016a4ddc8264b88191b7ff4fc54983908b"}},"id":"prt_f40255dc9001R4O7MHhpLUZJnd","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffe83jWKFM65pCjvi","messageID":"msg_f40252c00001CwDalivIwjB2sT"}}
